graphql_operation_files.content: query AllApiLimits {apiLimits: prisma_findManyUserApiLimit(orderBy: {id: asc}){id userId count createdAt updatedAt}}
query AllSubscriptions {subscriptions: prisma_findManyUserSubscription(orderBy: {id: asc}){id userId stripeCustomerId stripeSubscriptionId stripePriceId stripeCurrentPeriodEnd}}

mutation CreateSubscription($userId: String!, $stripeCustomerId: String, $stripeSubscriptionId: String, $stripePriceId: String, $stripeCurrentPeriodEnd: DateTime){prisma_createOneUserSubscription(data: {userId: $userId,stripeCustomerId: $stripeCustomerId,stripeSubscriptionId: $stripeSubscriptionId,stripePriceId: $stripePriceId,stripeCurrentPeriodEnd: $stripeCurrentPeriodEnd}){id}}
mutation UpdateApiLimit($id: String!, $count: Int!){prisma_updateOneUserApiLimit(where: {id: $id}, data: {count: {set: $count}}){id count}}

mutation UpdateSubscription($id: String!, $stripeCustomerId: String, $stripeSubscriptionId: String, $stripePriceId: String, $stripeCurrentPeriodEnd: DateTime){prisma_updateOneUserSubscription(where: {id: $id}, data: {stripeCustomerId: {set: $stripeCustomerId},stripeSubscriptionId: {set: $stripeSubscriptionId},stripePriceId: {set: $stripePriceId},stripeCurrentPeriodEnd: {set: $stripeCurrentPeriodEnd}}){id}}
